    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "This code has multiple conditions to check for. \r\n\r\n## Do This: \r\n- Run the code and observe the outputs for different dice rolls.\r\n- **Reflect**: How does the program decide which message to print?\r\n- **Modify** the elif condition to trigger if the dice lands on 5. ",
